=head2 LastModifiedTime => Str

The date and time that the model card was last modified.


=head2 ModelCardArn => Str

The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the model card.


=head2 ModelCardName => Str

The unique name of the model card.


=head2 ModelCardStatus => Str

The approval status of the model card within your organization.
Different organizations might have different criteria for model card
review and approval.

=over

=item *

C<Draft>: The model card is a work in progress.

=item *

C<PendingReview>: The model card is pending review.

=item *

C<Approved>: The model card is approved.

=item *

C<Archived>: The model card is archived. No more updates should be made
to the model card, but it can still be exported.

=back



=head2 ModelCardVersion => Int

The version of the model card.


=head2 ModelId => Str

The unique name (ID) of the model.


=head2 ModelPackageGroupName => Str

The model package group that contains the model package. Only relevant
for model cards created for model packages in the Amazon SageMaker
Model Registry.


=head2 RiskRating => Str

The risk rating of the model. Different organizations might have
different criteria for model card risk ratings. For more information,
see Risk ratings
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/latest/dg/model-cards-risk-rating.html).


=head2 SecurityConfig => L<Paws::SageMaker::ModelCardSecurityConfig>

